tion • Maintain eye health and healthy vision • Relieve symptoms of mild arthritis • Maintain heart health and cardiovascular health • Plus, it has additional benefits for skin and overall vitality Designed for those who want more from every capsule, Omega Platinum combines potency with convenience—so you can get more out of your day, your health, and your life. Product Format Capsule Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Heart and Cardiovascular Health Brain Health Eye Health Skin Health Mild Arthritis No Added Gluten No Added Wheat No Added Dairy Benefits & How To Use Benefits Available now at Chemist Warehouse. Shop here . Supports immune system health, vitality and general wellbeing. Maintains brain health and cognitive function. Supports nervous system health. Maintains eye health and healthy vision. Maintains skin health when dietary intake is inadequate. Relieves inflammation and supports symptoms of mild arthritis. Supports cardiovascular system health. Reduces free radicals from the body. 1 x Blackmores Omega Platinum = 4 x Blackmores Fish Oil 1000* *Omega platinum contains 1.28 g omega-3 compared with 300 mg in Fish Oil 1000 Dosage Adults Take 1 capsule once a day. For skin health and as an anti-inflammatory: Take 2 capsules once a day. Do not exceed 2 capsules in 24 hours. Take with food. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions before use. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains fish products, soya bean products and sulfites. Benefits Dosage Warnings Available now at Chemist Warehouse. Shop here . Supports immune system health, vitality and general wellbeing. Maintains brain health and cognitive function. Suppor