scover Blackmores Superkids!","descriptionEn":"Worried about your little one&#x27;s nutrient intake? Top up their diet with Blackmores&#x27; 99.5% sugar free kids multivitamin. Discover Blackmores Superkids!","descriptionTh":null,"extractedText":"Superkids™ Multi Chewables All Products Shop All Products New Products Best Sellers Vegan Certified Women&#x27;s Health Men&#x27;s Health Kid&#x27;s Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition By Category Arthritis, Joint & Bone Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutritional Oils Heart Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition Kids&#x27; Health Men&#x27;s Health Multivitamins Muscle Support Nails, Hair & Skin Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health By Ingredient Calcium CoQ10 Curcumin Echinacea Fish Oil & Omega 3 Glucosamine Iron Magnesium Probiotics Selenium Vitamin B Vitamin C Vitamin D Vitamin E Zinc Health Hub By Categories By Type Latest Articles Action Plans Arthritis, Bone & Joint Beauty & Skincare Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutrition Oils Heart & Cardiovascular Health Kids & Infant Health Men&#x27;s Health Muscle Support & Fitness Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Recipes Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health Action Plans Articles Recipes Latest Articles About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Pillars Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Contact us Ask A Naturopath Our Newsroom Blackmores Subscribe Search Home Chevron Icon Horizontal products Chevron Icon Horizontal Blackmores Superkids™ Multi Chewables Size Size 60 tablets BLACKMORES Superkids Multi Chewables are a multivitamin that helps support healthy growth and development, maintain healthy immune system function, and support general health and wellbeing. It also provides support for brain function and central nervous system development, while antioxidants help reduce free radicals formed in the body. With a natural strawberry-vanilla flavour, it’s a tasty option to help support kids’ daily wellbeing. Good health changes everything—help support kids’ daily wellness with BLACKMORES Superkids Multi Chewables. Product Format Chewable Tablet Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Kids Health Kids Development Brain Health General Health No Added Wheat No Added Gluten No Added Dairy No Added Yeast Halal Certified Benefits & How To Use Benefits Children can often have poor eating habits, which may make them vulnerable to nutritional shortfalls. Kids need sufficient energy and nutrients for normal physical and metabolic activities as well as to support growth and development. Whilst a balanced and varied diet is by far the best way for kids to get their nutrients, it has consistently been found that picky eaters have less variety in their diets than non-picky eaters, therefore a multivitamin may help to fill some critical nutritional gaps. Research undertaken in 2014-15 found that only one in twenty (5.1%) of Australian children were meeting the minimum number of serves of fruit and vegetables each day*. *http://www.abs.gov.au/ausstats Provides essential nutrients and antioxidants to support kids&#x27; healthy growth and development. Provides support for brain function. Supports central nervous system development. Supports general health and wellbeing. No added artificial sweeteners, colours or flavours. Dosage Children 2-12 years Chew (do not swallow whole) 1 tablet once a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Use only under adult supervision. Not recommended for children under 2 years. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. KEEP OUT OF REACH OF CHILDREN. Vitamin supplements should not replace a balanced diet. Excess consumption may have a laxative effect If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains soya bean products and sulfites. Benefits Dosage Warnings Children can often have poor eating habits, which may make them vulnerable to nutritional shortfalls. Kids need sufficient energy and nutrients for normal physical and metabolic activities as well as to support growth and development. Whilst a balanced and varied diet is by far the best way for kids to get their nutrients, it has consistently been found that picky eaters have less variety in their diets than non-picky eaters, therefore a multivitamin may help to fill some critical nutritional gaps. Research undertaken in 2014-15 found that only one in twenty (5.1%) of Australian children were meeting the minimum number of serves of fruit and vegetables each day*. *http://www.abs.gov.au/ausstats Provides essential nutrients and antioxidants to support kids&#x27; healthy growth and development. Provides support for brain function. Supports central nervous system development. Supports general health and wellbeing. No added artificial sweeteners, colours or flavours. Children 2-12 years Chew (do not swallow whole) 1 tablet once a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Use only under adult supervision. Not recommended for children under 2 years. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. KEEP OUT OF REACH OF CHILDREN. Vitamin supplements should not replace a balanced diet. Excess consumption may have a laxative effect If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains soya bean products and sulfites. Ingredient