blets are a great tasting, easy to chew vitamin C tablet that supports immune system health in adults and children.","descriptionTh":null,"extractedText":"Blackmores Bio C 500 Chewable Tablets All Products Shop All Products New Products Best Sellers Vegan Certified Women&#x27;s Health Men&#x27;s Health Kid&#x27;s Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition By Category Arthritis, Joint & Bone Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutritional Oils Heart Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition Kids&#x27; Health Men&#x27;s Health Multivitamins Muscle Support Nails, Hair & Skin Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health By Ingredient Calcium CoQ10 Curcumin Echinacea Fish Oil & Omega 3 Glucosamine Iron Magnesium Probiotics Selenium Vitamin B Vitamin C Vitamin D Vitamin E Zinc Health Hub By Categories By Type Latest Articles Action Plans Arthritis, Bone & Joint Beauty & Skincare Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutrition Oils Heart & Cardiovascular Health Kids & Infant Health Men&#x27;s Health Muscle Support & Fitness Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Recipes Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health Action Plans Articles Recipes Latest Articles About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Pillars Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Contact us Ask A Naturopath Our Newsroom Blackmores Subscribe Search Home Chevron Icon Horizontal products Chevron Icon Horizontal Blackmores Bio C® 500 Chewable Size Size 50 tablets 125 tablets 200 tablets Blackmores Bio C® 500 Chewable is sweetened with naturally derived ingredients and includes mineral ascorbates — a form of vitamin C that’s gentler on the stomach. This chewable formula contains vitamin C, which helps reduce free radical damage to body cells, supports immune system health, and supports general health and wellbeing. It also supports collagen formation and healthy immune system function in children aged 4 and over. Taken daily, it helps support vitamin C intake in a convenient format. Good health changes everything, make vitamin C part of your daily routine with Blackmores Bio C® 500 Chewable. Product Format Chewable Tablet Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Common Colds & Flu Immune System Health Antioxidant for Free Radical Damage General Health Halal Certified No Added Wheat No Added Dairy Benefits & How To Use Benefits Supports immune system health in adults & children. No artificial sweeteners - sweetened with naturally derived ingredients. Reduces the severity and duration of common cold symptoms. Buffered with mineral ascorbates to give you a vitamin C that are gentle on the stomach. Added bioflavonoids thought to support the efficacy of vitamin C. Supports general health and wellbeing. Contains antioxidant properties and helps reduce free radicals formed in the body. To relieve tiredness, support energy levels and immune health try Blackmores Run Down Rescue. Dosage Adults • Chew (do not swallow whole) 2 tablets once a day, or as prescribed by a healthcare professional. • Take with food. Children 4-17 years • For immune system health: Chew (do not swallow whole) 1 tablet once a day, or as prescribed by a healthcare professional. • Take with food. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, talk to your health professional before use. Use in children only under adult supervision. Not recommended for children under 4 years. KEEP OUT OF REACH OF CHILDREN. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. Dietary supplements can only be of assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains soya bean products and sulfites. Benefits Dosage Warnings Supports immune system health in adults & children. No artificial sweeteners - sweetened with naturally derived ingredients. Reduces the severity and duration of common cold symptoms. Buffered with mineral ascorbates to give you a vitamin C that are gentle on the stomach. Added bioflavonoids thought to support the efficacy of vitamin C. Supports general health and wellbeing. Contains antioxidant properties and helps reduce free radicals formed in the body. To relieve tiredness, support energy levels and immune health try Blackmores Run Down Rescue. Adults • Chew (do not swallow whole) 2 tablets once a day, or as prescribed by a healthcare professional. • Take with food. Children 4-17 years • For immune system health: Chew (do not swallow whole) 1 tablet once a day, or as prescribed by a healthcare professional. • Take with food. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, talk to your health professional before use. Use in children only under adult supervision. Not recommended for children under 4 years. KEEP OUT OF REACH OF CHILDREN. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. Dietary supplements can only be of assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains soya bean products and sulfites. The Blackmores Difference Ingredients Active ingredients per tablet: Ascorbic acid (vitamin C) 225 mg Sodium ascorbate 309.4 mg equivalent ascorbic acid (vitamin C) 275 mg Total vitamin C 500 mg Citrus bioflavonoids extract 10 mg Bio C® 500 Chewable Reviews Let&#x27;s stay in tou