 pregnancy and while breast-feeding, with vitamins, minerals and omega-3s.","descriptionTh":null,"extractedText":"Blackmores Pregnancy & Breast-Feeding Gold - Capsules (56) All Products Shop All Products New Products Best Sellers Vegan Certified Women&#x27;s Health Men&#x27;s Health Kid&#x27;s Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition By Category Arthritis, Joint & Bone Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutritional Oils Heart Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition Kids&#x27; Health Men&#x27;s Health Multivitamins Muscle Support Nails, Hair & Skin Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health By Ingredient Calcium CoQ10 Curcumin Echinacea Fish Oil & Omega 3 Glucosamine Iron Magnesium Probiotics Selenium Vitamin B Vitamin C Vitamin D Vitamin E Zinc Health Hub By Categories By Type Latest Articles Action Plans Arthritis, Bone & Joint Beauty & Skincare Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutrition Oils Heart & Cardiovascular Health Kids & Infant Health Men&#x27;s Health Muscle Support & Fitness Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Recipes Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health Action Plans Articles Recipes Latest Articles About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Pillars Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Contact us Ask A Naturopath Our Newsroom Blackmores Subscribe Search Home Chevron Icon Horizontal products Chevron Icon Horizontal Blackmores Pregnancy & Breast-Feeding Gold Size Size 60 capsules 120 capsules 180 capsules Formulated for before, during and after pregnancy, Blackmores Pregnancy & Breast-Feeding Gold provides a comprehensive blend of vitamins, minerals and omega-3 fatty acids to help maintain healthy pregnancy, support maternal health, and maintain vitamin and mineral levels in breastfeeding women. It also helps support healthy foetal development, support healthy foetal brain development, and prevent neural tube defects such as spina bifida and/or anencephaly. This formula includes iodine to support healthy thyroid hormone production and support healthy thyroid function during pregnancy. Good health changes everything - start your motherhood journey with nutritional support from Blackmores. Product Format Capsule Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Pregnancy Health Foetal Development No Added Yeast No Added Gluten No Added Wheat No Added Dairy Benefits & How To Use Benefits Supports a healthy pregnancy and healthy foetal development. Supports maternal health in pregnant and breastfeeding women. Blackmores Pregnancy & Breast-Feeding Gold provides 20 important nutrients in total including a daily dose of: 500 micrograms of folic acid which helps to prevent neural tube defects such as spina bifida when trying to conceive and during the first trimester of pregnancy. 150 micrograms of iodine to help support baby&#x27;s brain development. Lower constipation iron. Odourless and concentrated fish oil, rich in DHA for baby&#x27;s brain and nervous system development. Dosage Adults Take 2 capsules once a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Always talk to your health professional before taking multiple products for pregnancy. Do not exceed the stated dose except on medical advice. If you have had a baby with a neural tube defect / spina bifida, seek medical advice. This product contains selenium which is toxic in high doses. A daily dose of 150 microgram for adults of selenium from dietary supplements should not be exceeded. Vitamin supplements should not replace a balanced diet. Drink plenty of water. Advise your doctor of any medicine you take during pregnancy, particularly in your first trimester. If you are concerned about the health of yourself or your baby, talk to your health practitioner. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains sulfites, fish and soya bean products. Benefits Dosage Warnings Supports a healthy pregnancy and healthy foetal development. Supports maternal health in pregnant and breastfeeding women. Blackmores Pregnancy & Breast-Feeding Gold provides 20 important nutrients in total including a daily dose of: 500 micrograms of folic acid which helps to prevent neural tube defects such as spina bifida when trying to conceive and during the first trimester of pregnancy. 150 micrograms of iodine to help support baby&#x27;s brain development. Lower constipation iron. Odourless and concentrated fish oil, rich in DHA for baby&#x27;s brain and nervous system development. Adults Take 2 capsules once a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Always talk to your health professional before taking multiple products for pregnancy. Do not exceed the stated dose except on medical advice. If you have had a baby with a neural tube defect / spina bifida, seek medical advice. This product contains selenium which is toxic in high doses. A daily dose of 150 microgram for adults of selenium from dietary supplements should not be exceeded. Vitamin supplements should not replace a balanced diet. Drink plenty of water. Advise your doctor of any medicine you take during pregnancy, particularly in your first trimester. If you are concerned about the health of yourself or your baby, talk to your health practitioner. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains sulfites, fish and soya bean products. The Blackmores Difference Ingredients Active ingredients per capsule: Folic acid 250 micrograms Potassium iodide 98.3 micrograms equivalent iodine 75 micrograms Concentrated fish omega-3 triglycerides 250 mg containing omega-3 triglycerides 150 mg equivalent eicosapentaenoic acid (EPA) 25 mg equivalent docosahexaenoic acid (DHA) 125 mg Iron (II) glycinate 19.2 mg equivalent iron 5 mg Colecalciferol 12.5 micrograms equivalent vitamin D 500 IU Nicotinamide 9 mg Ascorbic acid (vitamin C) 30 mg Calcium carbonate 125 mg equivalent calcium 50 mg Biotin 15 micrograms Zinc oxide 6.8 mg equivalent zinc 5.5 mg Heavy magnesium oxide 58.1 mg equivalent magnesium 35 mg Selenomethionine 81.3 micrograms equivalent selenium 32.5 micrograms Chromium picolinate 121 micrograms equivalent chromium 15 micrograms Thiamine nitrate (vitamin B1) 700 micrograms Riboflavin (vitamin B2) 700 micrograms Calcium pantothenate 2.7 mg equivalent pantothenic acid (vitamin B5) 2.5 mg Pyridoxine hydrochloride 1.2 mg equivalent pyridoxine (vitamin B6) 950 micrograms Cyanocobalamin (vitamin B12) 1.3 micrograms d-alpha-tocopherol 3.5 mg equivalent vitamin E 5.2 IU Betacarotene 2.4 mg Show More Pregnancy & Breast-Feeding Gold Reviews Let&#x27;s stay in touch Instagram Facebook TikTok LinkedIn Back To Top About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Approach Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Our Newsroom About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Approach Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Our Newsroom Our Brands & Products Shop Our Products Shop Best Sellers BioCeuticals Blackmores Professional Blackmores Institute Blackmores Education Our Brands & Products Shop Our Products Shop Best Sellers BioCeuticals Blackmores Professional Blackmores Institute