;s Health Men&#x27;s Health Kid&#x27;s Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition By Category Arthritis, Joint & Bone Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutritional Oils Heart Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition Kids&#x27; Health Men&#x27;s Health Multivitamins Muscle Support Nails, Hair & Skin Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health By Ingredient Calcium CoQ10 Curcumin Echinacea Fish Oil & Omega 3 Glucosamine Iron Magnesium Probiotics Selenium Vitamin B Vitamin C Vitamin D Vitamin E Zinc Health Hub By Categories By Type Latest Articles Action Plans Arthritis, Bone & Joint Beauty & Skincare Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutrition Oils Heart & Cardiovascular Health Kids & Infant Health Men&#x27;s Health Muscle Support & Fitness Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Recipes Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health Action Plans Articles Recipes Latest Articles About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Pillars Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Contact us Ask A Naturopath Our Newsroom Blackmores Subscribe Search Home Chevron Icon Horizontal products Chevron Icon Horizontal Blackmores Vitamin B6 Size Size 40 tablets Blackmores Vitamin B6 is a sustained release formula designed to relieve mood changes associated with premenstrual tension. It also helps support nervous system function and assists protein synthesising the body and temporarily relieves mild fluid retention contributing to daily wellbeing. This one-a-day formula supports general health, energy level, and helps ease the symptoms that may arise in the lead-up to your period. Blackmores Vitamin B6 is ideal for women looking for natural, gradual nutrient support throughout their cycle. Good health changes everything—support your energy levels and mood swings associated with premenstrual tension with Blackmores Vitamin B6. Product Format Tablet Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Premenstrual Tension (PMT) No Added Yeast No Added Gluten No Added Dairy No Added Soya Bean Benefits & How To Use Benefits Helps to relieve pre-menstrual tension symptoms including: -Mild fluid retention -Irritability Dosage Adults At the first sign of pre-menstrual symptoms and during menstruation, take 1 tablet (swallow whole) once a day. Take with food. For short-term use during menstruation only. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. WARNING - Stop taking this medication if you experience tingling, burning or numbness and see your healthcare practitioner as soon as possible. (Contains vitamin B6) WARNING – This medication may be dangerous when used in large amounts or for a long time. If symptoms persist consult your health professional. Supplements can only be of assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. Do not use during pregnancy or breastfeeding. Talk to your health professional before taking multiple products containing vitamin B6. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains sulfites and phenylalanine. Benefits Dosage Warnings Helps to relieve pre-menstrual tension symptoms including: -Mild fluid retention -Irritability Adults At the first sign of pre-menstrual symptoms and during menstruation, take 1 tablet (swallow whole) once a day. Take with food. For short-term use during menstruation only. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. WARNING - Stop taking this medication if you experience tingling, burning or numbness and see your healthcare practitioner as soon as possible. (Contains vitamin B6) W