llow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Heart and Cardiovascular Health Brain Health Eye Health Skin Health No Added Gluten No Added Wheat No Added Dairy Benefits & How To Use Benefits Supports immune system health and general wellbeing. Maintains brain health and cognitive function. Supports nervous system health. Maintains eye health and healthy vision. Maintains skin health when dietary intake is inadequate. Helps maintain a healthy heart, cardiovascular system and healthy blood lipids. Relieves symptoms of mild arthritis. Relieves inflammation. Reduces free radicals formed in the body (antioxidant). Dosage Take only ONE dose recommendation, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Adults - Take 1 capsule once a day For skin health and as an anti-inflammatory: Adults - Take 2 capsules once a day. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, or on warfarin therapy, talk to your health professional before use. Dietary supplements can only be of assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains fish products, soya bean products and sulfites. Store below 30°c. Keep out of direct sunlight in a cool, dry place. DO NOT USE IF CAP SEALIS BROKENOR MISSING. Benefits Dosage Warnings Supports immune system health and general wellbeing. Maintains brain health and cognitive function. Supports nervous system health. Maintains eye health and healthy vision. Maintains skin health when dietary intake is inadequate. Helps maintain a healthy heart, cardiovascular system and healthy blood lipids. Relieves symptoms of mild arthritis. Relieves inflammation. Reduces free radicals 