 Garlic + C tablets support immune system health and helps relieve symptoms of mild upper respiratory tract infections.","descriptionTh":null,"extractedText":"Blackmores Horseradish Garlic + C Tablets All Products Shop All Products New Products Best Sellers Vegan Certified Women&#x27;s Health Men&#x27;s Health Kid&#x27;s Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition By Category Arthritis, Joint & Bone Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutritional Oils Heart Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition Kids&#x27; Health Men&#x27;s Health Multivitamins Muscle Support Nails, Hair & Skin Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health By Ingredient Calcium CoQ10 Curcumin Echinacea Fish Oil & Omega 3 Glucosamine Iron Magnesium Probiotics Selenium Vitamin B Vitamin C Vitamin D Vitamin E Zinc Health Hub By Categories By Type Latest Articles Action Plans Arthritis, Bone & Joint Beauty & Skincare Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutrition Oils Heart & Cardiovascular Health Kids & Infant Health Men&#x27;s Health Muscle Support & Fitness Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Recipes Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health Action Plans Articles Recipes Latest Articles About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Pillars Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Contact us Ask A Naturopath Our Newsroom Blackmores Subscribe Search Home Chevron Icon Horizontal products Chevron Icon Horizontal Blackmores Horseradish Garlic + C Size Size 50 tablets 90 tablets Good health changes everything - support your immune health with Blackmores Horseradish Garlic + C. This formula contains garlic and horseradish, traditionally used in Western herbal medicine to relieve symptoms of mild upper respiratory tract infections and nasal congestion. Vitamin C provides additional support to maintain immune system health and offers antioxidant benefits by helping reduce free radicals formed in the body. Ideal for seasonal immune support, this triple-action blend also helps reduce the duration and severity of common cold symptoms. With a combination of time-tested herbs and nutrients, Blackmores Horseradish Garlic + C supports your body&#x27;s natural defences. Product Format Tablet Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Immune System Health Congestion Upper Respiratory Tract Common Colds & Flu No Added Yeast No Added Dairy Benefits & How To Use Benefits With vitamin C to support immune system health. Contains garlic and horseradish which are traditionally used in Western herbal medicine to: -Act as a decongestant to relieve nasal congestion. -Relieve symptoms of mild upper respiratory tract infections. Reduces duration and symptom severity of common colds. Supports general health and wellbeing. Dosage Adults Take 1 tablet twice a day with meals or as prescribed by a health professional. Children under 18 years Only as prescribed by a health professional. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Adults only. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. Dietary supplements can only be of assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. Do not use during pregnancy and breastfeeding. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains soya bean products. Benefits Dosage Warnings With vitamin C to support immune system health. Contains garlic and horseradish which are traditionally used in Western herbal medicine to: -Act as a decongestant to relieve nasal congestion. -Relieve symptoms of mild upper respiratory tract infections. Reduces duration and symptom severity of common colds. Supports general health and wellbeing. Adults Take 1 tablet twice a day with meals or as prescribed by a health professional. Children under 18 years Only as prescribed by a health professional. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Adults only. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. Dietary supplements can only be of assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. Do not use during pregnancy and breastfeeding. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains soya bean products. Ingredients Active ingredients per tablet: Armoracia rusticana (horseradish) extract dry conc. 90 mg equivalent dry root 1.8 g Allium sativum (garlic) extract dry conc. 50 mg equivalent fresh bulb 1 g Ascorbic acid (vitamin C) 500 mg Trigonella foenum-graecum (fenugreek) extract dry conc. 4 mg equivalent dry seed 50 mg Horseradish Garlic + C Reviews Let&#x27;s stay in touch Instagram Facebook TikTok LinkedIn Back To Top About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Approach Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Our Newsroom About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Approach Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Our Newsroom Our Brands & Products Shop Our Products Shop Best Sellers BioCeuticals Blackmores Professional Blackmores Institute Blackmores Education Our Brands & Products Shop Our Products Shop Best Sellers BioCeuticals Blackmores Professional Blackmores Institute Blackmores Education International Markets China Hong Kong SAR iHerb Indonesia Korea Malaysia New Zealand Singapore Taiwan Region Thailand Vietnam International Markets China Hong Kong SAR iHerb Indonesia Korea M