il 1000 Odourless Capsules All Products Shop All Products New Products Best Sellers Vegan Certified Women&#x27;s Health Men&#x27;s Health Kid&#x27;s Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition By Category Arthritis, Joint & Bone Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutritional Oils Heart Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition Kids&#x27; Health Men&#x27;s Health Multivitamins Muscle Support Nails, Hair & Skin Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health By Ingredient Calcium CoQ10 Curcumin Echinacea Fish Oil & Omega 3 Glucosamine Iron Magnesium Probiotics Selenium Vitamin B Vitamin C Vitamin D Vitamin E Zinc Health Hub By Categories By Type Latest Articles Action Plans Arthritis, Bone & Joint Beauty & Skincare Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutrition Oils Heart & Cardiovascular Health Kids & Infant Health Men&#x27;s Health Muscle Support & Fitness Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Recipes Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health Action Plans Articles Recipes Latest Articles About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Pillars Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Contact us Ask A Naturopath Our Newsroom Blackmores Subscribe Search Home Chevron Icon Horizontal products Chevron Icon Horizontal Blackmores Fish Oil 1000 Odourless Size Size 200 capsules 400 capsules Blackmores Fish Oil 1000 Odourless provides 300 mg of omega-3 per capsule to help maintain your overall wellbeing. It is formulated to support heart , brain and eye health, and also helps support cognitive function and nervous system health. This product also helps support skin health and general health and wellbeing. Omega-3 fatty acids are important for various functions in the body, and this odourless formulation is designed for individuals who may not consume fish regularly. Taken daily, Blackmores Fish Oil 1000 Odourless supports multiple areas of health as part of your daily wellness routine. Whether you&#x27;re supporting your heart, brain or skin health, Blackmores Fish Oil 1000 Odourless delivers essential omega-3s - because good health changes everything. Product Format Capsule Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Kids Development Heart and Cardiovascular Health Brain Health Skin Health No Added Yeast No Added Gluten No Added Wheat No Added Dairy Benefits & How To Use Benefits Maintains heart, skin, eye and brain health. Supports general health and wellbeing. Supports healthy growth and development in children. Natural source of omega-3 eicosapentaenoic acid (EPA) and docosahexaenoic acid (DHA). Ideal if you don&#x27;t eat fish 2-3 times per week. Rigorously tested for mercury, dioxins and PCBs. Dosage Take only one recommendation. Take with food. Adults For heart, skin and general health: Take 2 capsules once a day. For brain and eye health: Take 3 capsules once a day. Children 1+ years For healthy growth and development : Give 2 capsules once a day Children unable to swallow - pierce the capsule, squeeze the content into milk, juice or cereal and consume immediately. Do not swallow whole. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Use in children only under adult supervision. Not recommended for children under 1 year. KEEP OUT OF REACH OF CHILDREN. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains fish, sulfites and soya bean products. Benefits Dosage Warnings Maintains heart, skin, eye and brain health. Supports general health and wellbeing. Supports healthy growth and development in children. Natural source of