immune system and reduce common cold symptoms.","descriptionTh":null,"extractedText":"Blackmores Bio C 1000 Tablets All Products Shop All Products New Products Best Sellers Vegan Certified Women&#x27;s Health Men&#x27;s Health Kid&#x27;s Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition By Category Arthritis, Joint & Bone Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutritional Oils Heart Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition Kids&#x27; Health Men&#x27;s Health Multivitamins Muscle Support Nails, Hair & Skin Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health By Ingredient Calcium CoQ10 Curcumin Echinacea Fish Oil & Omega 3 Glucosamine Iron Magnesium Probiotics Selenium Vitamin B Vitamin C Vitamin D Vitamin E Zinc Health Hub By Categories By Type Latest Articles Action Plans Arthritis, Bone & Joint Beauty & Skincare Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutrition Oils Heart & Cardiovascular Health Kids & Infant Health Men&#x27;s Health Muscle Support & Fitness Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Recipes Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health Action Plans Articles Recipes Latest Articles About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Pillars Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Contact us Ask A Naturopath Our Newsroom Blackmores Subscribe Search Home Chevron Icon Horizontal products Chevron Icon Horizontal Blackmores Bio C® 1000 Size Size 31 tablets 62 tablets 150 tablets Blackmores Bio C® 1000 is a high-potency vitamin C supplement formulated with mineral ascorbates for gentle absorption. It helps reduce the duration and severity of common cold symptoms, support immune system health, and maintain collagen formation and wound healing. Its antioxidant properties also help reduce free radicals and free radical damage. Good health changes everything - support your defences with Blackmores Bio C® 1000. Product Format Tablet Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Collagen Formation Antioxidant for Free Radical Damage Immune System Health Common Colds & Flu No Added Yeast No Added Gluten No Added Wheat No Added Dairy No Added Soya Bean Benefits & How To Use Benefits Reduces the severity and duration of common cold symptoms. High strength vitamin C. Buffered with mineral ascorbates to give you a vitamin C that&#x27;s gentle on the stomach. Added bioflavonoids thought to support the efficacy of vitamin C. Contains rosehips and acerola which are sources of vitamin C . Supports immune system health. Contains antioxidant properties and helps reduce free radicals formed in the body. Supports general health and wellbeing. Dosage Adults Take 1 tablet once a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, talk to your health professional before use. Adults only. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. Dietary supplements can only be of assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains sulfites. Benefits Dosage Warnings Reduces the severity and duration of common cold symptoms. High strength vitamin C. Buffered with mineral ascorbates to give you a vitamin C that&#x27;s gentle on the stomach. Added bioflavonoids thought to support the efficacy of vitamin C. Contains rosehips and acerola which are sources of vitamin C . Supports immune system health. Contains antioxidant properties and helps reduce free radicals formed in the body. Supports general health and wellbeing. Adu