  ('b875adb9-39af-445a-8c28-14b9467ce777'::uuid, '27da6564-ae99-4839-8061-362a90f946cb'::uuid, null, 'product_updated', 'admin_bulk_ignore_no_parseable_facts', '{"id":"27da6564-ae99-4839-8061-362a90f946cb","title":"Blackmores Valerian Forte","region":"TH","source":"manufacturer_import","status":"pending_review","brand_id":"40e4806a-5049-4668-8d29-ab36a31202dd","category":null,"currency":"THB","platform":"manual","title_en":"Blackmores Valerian Forte","title_th":null,"image_url":"https://images.contentstack.io/v3/assets/blt948bd74310fc0ad0/blt3bcf0a1cf2adff16/68bfc0cf2899fa7706939732/93808545-1.webp","brand_name":"blackmores","created_at":"2026-05-21T13:09:48.940915+00:00","source_url":"https://www.blackmores.com.au/products/valerian-forte","updated_at":"2026-05-22T00:30:35.645379+00:00","admin_notes":null,"description":"Blackmores Valerian Forte contains valerian, which is traditionally used in Western Herbal medicine to supports refreshing sleep","product_url":"https://www.blackmores.com.au/products/valerian-forte","label_status":"missing","price_amount":null,"product_kind":"supplement","description_en":"Blackmores Valerian Forte contains valerian, which is traditionally used in Western Herbal medicine to supports refreshing sleep","description_th":null,"normalized_url":"https://www.blackmores.com.au/products/valerian-forte","current_version":1,"fda_verified_at":null,"price_cached_at":null,"source_snapshot":{"dosage":"for use. Read the","locale":"en","parser":"blackmores_structured_ingredients_v2","titleEn":"Blackmores Valerian Forte","htmlLength":166224,"validation":{"status":"failed","reasons":["no_canonical_match","no_dosed_facts"],"summary":"No usable per-serving product facts.","checkedAt":"2026-05-22T00:30:35.643Z","matchableFactCount":0},"description":"Blackmores Valerian Forte contains valerian, which is traditionally used in Western Herbal medicine to supports refreshing sleep","descriptionEn":"Blackmores Valerian Forte contains valerian, which is traditionally used in Western Herbal medicine to supports refreshing sleep","descriptionTh":null,"extractedText":"Valerian Forte All Products Shop All Products New Products Best Sellers Vegan Certified Women&#x27;s Health Men&#x27;s Health Kid&#x27;s Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition By Category Arthritis, Joint & Bone Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutritional Oils Heart Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition Kids&#x27; Health Men&#x27;s Health Multivitamins Muscle Support Nails, Hair & Skin Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health By Ingredient Calcium CoQ10 Curcumin Echinacea Fish Oil & Omega 3 Glucosamine Iron Magnesium Probiotics Selenium Vitamin B Vitamin C Vitamin D Vitamin E Zinc Health Hub By Categories By Type Latest Articles Action Plans Arthritis, Bone & Joint Beauty & Skincare Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutrition Oils Heart & Cardiovascular Health Kids & Infant Health Men&#x27;s Health Muscle Support & Fitness Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Recipes Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health Action Plans Articles Recipes Latest Articles About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Pillars Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Contact us Ask A Naturopath Our Newsroom Blackmores Subscribe Search Home Chevron Icon Horizontal products Chevron Icon Horizontal Blackmores Valerian Forte Size Size 30 tablets 60 tablets Blackmores Valerian Forte provides a concentrated valerian extract in a convenient one-a-day dose. Traditionally used in Western herbal medicine, valerian is known to induce sleep, reduce the time to fall asleep, and relieve disturbed sleep. It also helps maintain refreshing sleep for improved nightly rest. Taken daily, this herbal formula supports deep sleep. Good health changes everything—rest easy with Blackmores Valerian Forte. Product Format Tablet Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Sleep No Added Yeast No Added Gluten No Added Wheat No Added Dairy No Added Soya Bean Benefits & How To Use Benefits Helps reduce time to fall asleep. Supports refreshing sleep. Reduces restless sleep. Valerian is traditionally used in Western herbal medicine to enhance sleep quality. Helps mind relaxation. One-a-day dose. Dosage Adults Take 1 tablet once a day, 30 minutes to one hour before bedtime. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Do not use during pregnancy or breastfeeding. In rare cases, valerian may harm the liver. Stop use and see a doctor if you have yellowing skin/eyes or unusual; fatigue, nausea, appetite loss, abdominal pain, dark urine or itching. May cause drowsiness, if affected do not drive a vehicle or operate machinery. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. If you have any pre-existing conditions, are on any medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains sulfites. Benefits Dosage Warnings Helps reduce time to fall asleep. Supports refreshing sleep. Reduces restless sleep. Valerian is traditionally used in Western herbal medicine to enhance sleep quality. Helps mind relaxation. One-a-day dose. Adults Take 1 tablet once a day, 30 minutes to one hour before bedtime. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Do not use during pregnancy or breastfeeding. In rare cases, valerian may harm the liver. Stop use and see a doctor if you have yellowing skin/eyes or unusual; fatigue, nausea, appetite loss, abdominal pain, dark urine or itching. May cause drowsiness, if affected do not drive a vehicle or operate machinery. If symptoms persist, talk to your health p